snippet.title: Celebrity Page TV
snippet.description: CelebrityPage.com is one of the fastest-growing pop culture online platforms. Our newsrooms are based in New York City, Los Angeles and Las Vegas, where we’re keeping you updated on the latest trending and pop culture stories from around the world. You can also catch us on TV! Our television show, Celebrity Page TV, airs during the weekends nationwide on REELZ cable channel, along with local TV stations across the country. Our shows and videos can also be found on YouTube on all connected TV devices. For the latest entertainment updates 24/7, follow us on all social media @celebritypagetv. To win giveaways and to join our Celebrity Page Insider Club, visit our website at celebritypage.com.
